    "Under their national energy strategy, they aim to have 52% of their installed electricity production capacity come from renewables by 2030.",
    "This includes a significant contribution from wind energy.",
    "Hence, your project aligns well with the national policy.",
    "In summary, while the expected increase in temperature and decrease in wind speed could pose some challenges to your wind farm project, the supportive regulatory environment and the general decrease in precipitation could provide some advantages.",
